	* src/core/proxy.c, src/core/proxy.h: New files.
	A simple proxy client implementation. Currently support SOCKSv4 and
	SOCKSv5 proxy.

	* configure.ac, src/core/Makefile.am: Configure option and build
	instructions for proxy.

